wiki.content:
"I'm not to sure what i did on my computer, but one day it started advertising to me differently. Up until then it advertised to me specifically as a heterosexual male. I don't know what i typed into Google or whatever... I thought 'oh my god how interesting my computer thinks i'm gay today', What a ridiculous way to start a song." - Brian Molko
